sequenceDiagram
    %%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
    participant Agent as Agent Execution
    participant OTel as Cloud Trace (OTel)
    participant Eval as Vertex EvalTask
    participant BQ as BigQuery (Sink)
    participant Looker as Looker Dashboards
    
    Agent->>OTel: Emit Spans (Latency, Tokens)
    Agent->>Eval: Send Prompt/Response Pairs
    Eval-->>Eval: Score via Custom Rubric (1-5 Ratings)
    Eval->>BQ: pd.DataFrame.to_gbq() append
    note right of BQ: Data schema includes Timestamp,<br/>Agent_Version, and Eval Scores.
    Looker->>BQ: Query average scores grouped by time
    Looker->>OTel: (Optional) Correlate with operational data
